{"type":"system","subtype":"hook_response","hook_id":"63566349-cbba-418d-b5d2-195660d4419d","hook_name":"SessionStart:startup","hook_event":"SessionStart","output":"=== HANDOFF ===\nWrite next handoff to: /home/skynet/cabala-dos-caminhos/.remember/remember.md\n\n=== REMEMBER ===\nHistory in .remember/: now.md (buffer), today-*.md (daily), recent.md (7d), archive.md (old), core-memories.md (key moments). Search on user request.\n\n=== MEMORY ===\n--- today-2026-06-11.md ---\n## 01:01-01:17 | main\nRead app_spec.txt/VISION.md/TODO.md; marked R-025 in_progress; ran exa MCP searches (WebSearch 400'd) for 6 tech decisions D-030..D-036; wrote tech/stack_v1.md — Fases 0-3 done, Fase 4 (Tech Stack) started. Fixed 3 orchestrator.sh bugs (set -e crash, missing prompt, --resume arg); wired max-autonomy (hard stop → meta-review cycle, ctx-aware bootstrap) + QA STEPS 10/11/12 + FASE 7 (F-100..F-105 feats); loop ran 7h/16 sessions/12-12 RQs done/2-6 Fase 1 done; detached via daemon PID 1580801 (parent=init) survives session close; set up dev DB (DATABASE_URL/JWT_SECRET/pgvector) for register flow; added RQ-026+R-029 5-pillar vision (Num Cabalística+Tântrica+Odu+Astrol+I Ching) + CONTEXT HYGIENE section in coding_prompt.md; created Plans.md (stop-hook compliance); PLN-013 logged Mandala size feedback. Supervised active loop (20 sessions, 235 files +22835/-834 lines, 35 commits); delivered report covering 12 RQs Fase 0 + R-020..R-024 synth/persona/UX; R-025 (tech_decisions.md 1179 lines, D-030..D-039: Next16+pgvector+Prisma7+OpenAI+Stripe+SSE) done; stopped BG loop PIDs 1580801/1580849/1543759/1619289; started R-030 (Akasha Core Algorithm TS puro, 90min, $12.75) inline.\n\n## 10:20 | main\nSec review R-030 Akasha Core diff (packages/akasha-core/src/akasha-core.ts + .test.ts + index.ts) — no findings: `calcular()` no callers in apps/, no I/O sinks (no shell/FS/SQL/HTTP/eval/log); `loadEngines()` hardcoded pkg-name string literals (bundler directives, not dynamic load); Zod schema va