- Apps on Google Play\nURL: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?hl=en_US&id=world.iching.iching\nPublished: N/A\nAuthor: N/A\nHighlights:\nHello! I'm Illia, a developer from Ukraine 🇺🇦, and I've created I Ching AI – a unique app inspired by the ancient wisdom of the Book of Changes (I Ching).📖 What is the I Ching?The Book of Changes is a millennia-old source of wisdom that describes 64 hexagrams ䷞ – patterns of life situations with warnings ⚠️ and advice 💡 on how to act. It has inspired philosophers like Confucius and continues to help people find answers to complex life questions.🔮 How does I Ching AI work?You can interact with the app in three unique modes:💬➜䷞ Identify – describe your situation, and the app will analyze it, determine the most fitting hexagram, and explain why it matches your case.䷞➜💬 Interpret – if you already know your hexagram, just enter its number with your personal question, and the app will interpret its meaning in the context of your situation.🎲➜䷞ Random – describe your situation, and the app will select a hexagram randomly, giving you an unexpected perspective and new insights.🌟 What can you do with I Ching AI?✦ Determine a hexagram ✨ and get guidance for your current situation.✦ Keep a diary 📔 – save your queries and AI responses to track life events (one query per day).✦ Study the I Ching 📚 – explore detailed descriptions of all 64 hexagrams.✦ Observe others 🌍 – see in real-time which hexagrams people around the world are receiving.👤 Who is it for?I Ching AI is a helper for those who:✦ Feel anxious or uncertain 😟 and seek clarity.✦ Want to make informed decisions ⚖️ in challenging situations.✦ Aim to understand themselves better 🪷 through the lens of the Book of Changes.If anxiety or uncertainty keeps you awake at night 🌙, describe your feelings in the app – and receive a hexagram to help you find calm and the right path forward 🕊️.💡 How to get the best results?✦ Describe your situation in as much detail as possible ✍️, including your emotions ❤️ and attitude toward it.✦ This helps the AI select the most accurate hexagram and provide helpful advice.🎯 Why is I Ching AI special?✦ Three unique dialogue modes 💬➜䷞ | ䷞➜💬 | 🎲➜䷞✦ Available in 11 languages 🌐✦ Supports light and dark themes 🌞🌚✦ Intuitive and easy to use 👍👉 Try it now!Download I Ching AI and discover the wisdom of the Book of Changes 🔮.If you notice a bug 🐞 or have ideas 💡 to improve the app, write to me – together, we can make it even better!\n\n---\n\nTitle: ‎I Ching: Hexagram Dreams App - App Store\nURL: https://apps.apple.com/sk/app/i-ching-hexagram-dreams/id6480458200\nPublished: N/A\nAuthor: N/A\nHighlights:\njournal, use question suggestions coach to ask better questions, and get a custom divination interpretation for every I Ching reading. Track your patterns over time with advanced analytics no other I Ching app offers, and build a consistent practice you will actually keep. Use the I Ching as a daily reflection practice. Cast with intention. Explore the meaning. Make decisions with perspective. Whether it is a relationship, a career crossroads, or a feeling you can not quite name, the I Ching helps you slow down and see your situation from a wiser angle. HOW IT WORKS ◆ Focus on your question - write down your concern. The quality of your question shapes the quality of your hexagram reading. ◆ Cast your hexagram - use the traditional 3 coin toss method line by line. ◆ Interpret your I Ching reading - explore the primary hexagram, changing lines, and the resulting hexagram. ◆ Reflect and save - add personal notes, save your reading in your spiritual journal, and revisit it later to see how things unfolded. STATISTICS FOR YOUR READINGS JOURNAL Once you have a few readings logged, Hexagram Dreams turns your journal into a quiet mirror. Here is a small part what it shows you: - Total number of readings you have cast - Your average pace (readings per week) - Your best streak of consecutive days - When your last reading was, and the longest pause you have taken There are much more advanced stats. QUESTION COACH Try question suggestions for inspiration. Try rephrase question feature to change the question. Try follow up questions for more ideas. CUSTOM READING Hexagram explanations are sometimes cryptic, try the Custom interpretation feature. PRACTICE REMINDER Set daily or weekly reminders to build a consistent I Ching reflection habit and maintain your streak. Configurable from settings or from the app sidebar. BACKUP Login if you want your history to be synced to cloud. That way you're safe if you change phones, or want to use it from another device. Same can be achieved with exporting the database, but you have to remember to do it manually. You can also export your readings to pdf or csv (top right menu from diary screen) ARE YOU A TRADITIONAL I CHING PRACTITIONER? If you prefer to use yarrow stalks or your own coins for casting, and prefer to read original Zhouyi, or Wilhelm-Baynes translation? You can still use this app solely for keeping a journal of your readings (use manual input to enter your hexagrams). One benefit is keeping track of your readings, so you can reflect on them later on. Other benefit is the Statistics that Hexagram Dreams offers you. ABOUT THE I CHING Also known as the Yi Jing, Yijing, or Book of Changes, the I Ching is an ancient Chinese divination system built around 64 hexagrams,"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_function_p7vw6nqjp2z9_1","session_id":"e7c48987-b5d5-4f27-9d18-efac56ac5754","uuid":"246798eb-d2c9-45aa-b4c9-377b1b6849b0","timestamp":"2026-06-11T15:02:30.750Z","subagent_type":"general-purpose","task_description":"Research I Ching 64 sources"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"call_function_kfvnlygdsj1n_3","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Title: Gene Keys – a simple introduction - Gene Keys\nURL: https://genekeys.com/articles/gene-keys-a-simple-introduction/\nPublished: 2018-08-14T06:49:53.000Z\nAuthor: Unknown Member\nHighlights:\nMy name is Richard Rudd and I was that young man, and shortly after that terrifying encounter I inexplicably began to experience visions. Turning away from a career in a highly reputable family wine business, I took the road less travelled and set off on a global quest to try and find\n[...]\nthat now burned inside me. It took 25 years before the visions came into a sharp focus. One day\n[...]\nised inside me\n[...]\nall the systems I had studied and all the teachers I had learned from\n[...]\nA vast book just came\n[...]\nI am sure that\n[...]\nhave the experience\n[...]\nbook coming alive as\n[...]\nThis is where the Gene Keys book comes in. Consisting of 64 human behavioural archetypes, Gene Keys is a codebook of the pitfalls and potentials of human consciousness. Each archetype or ‘Gene Key’ has 3 levels of frequency known as Shadows (victim patterns), Gifts (creative genius) and Siddhis (divine manifestations). As you contemplate Gene Keys over time it takes you on a deep personal journey into your specific Shadow patterns in order that you can unlock their latent higher potential. In the spirit of the original I Ching, Gene Keys teaches from within you by reflecting back the level of your authenticity and awareness as you go about your everyday life. This is an experiential teaching that can trigger a process of profound illumination in your life.\n[...]\nAn additional dimension to the book comes from a unique online profiling system that provides each person with a free ‘Hologenetic Profile’. Your Profile is based on a holographic understanding of the cosmos in which the time and place of your birth is seen as having a direct connection to your genetic imprinting. Your Profile displays 3 sequences of Gene Keys that relate specifically to patterns in your life. One unlocks your genius, one reveals the higher purpose of your relationships and one aligns you to the forces of prosperity. Together, these sequences form a ‘Golden Path’ – a personalised inner voyage towards higher consciousness. Using the Gene Keys book as your map and your Profile as a compass, your daily life itself becomes the Golden Path towards a higher potential.\n[...]\nThe Gene Keys teachings are for the seeker who is tired of collecting more information and who doesn’t want to follow another teacher or external teaching. The Gene Keys are an interior teaching whose purpose is to increase your awareness through sustained contemplation of both your Shadow patterns and your purest essence. They are a spiritual teaching for modern life that you shape to fit your life, and like the original I Ching, they are a journey of Self Illumination that brings personal transformation right into your daily life.\n\n---\n\nTitle: How to read your profile - Gene Keys\nURL: https://genekeys.com/how-to-read-your-profile/\nPublished: 2019-06-23T01:44:49.000Z\nAuthor: N/A\nHighlights:\nIn this introductory video with founder Richard Rudd, each element of the profile is explained, and you are invited to explore all the details and layers hidden inside your own profile. It also features some wonderful animations to help guide you in your first step on your Gene Keys journey!\n[...]\nYour Gene Keys Profile is a personalised map of your inner being. It shows you the archetypal patterns that block the natural manifestation of your Genius (Shadows), and how to transform these patterns into your Gifts.\n[...]\nIn the Gene Keys Synthesis, the vibratory rate of your aura is mirrored in three frequency ‘bands’ known as the Shadow, the Gift and the Siddhi. Although there are in fact many layers or bandwidths of frequency, this threefold language makes the Gene Keys simple to understand, contemplate and ultimately embody. The three frequency bands are laid out precisely through the Spectrum of Consciousness – the linguistic map of the 64 Gene Keys and their frequency bands.\n[...]\nIn each Sphere of your Profile you will see a number between 1 and 64. This number represents your unique Gene Key for that Sphere, which is determined by the date, time and place of your birth. We can awaken the higher components of each of our Gene Keys by contemplating them over time and in sequence.\n[...]\nEach of the Sequences in your Gene Keys Profile offers a possibility to unfold a specific aspect of your higher purpose in life. Even though these are viewed as separate sequences encoding aspects of your destiny, they are all interconnected. This means that as you contemplate your sequences in the framework of your daily life, you will activate all aspects of the Gene Keys Profile simultaneously, allowing you to witness dynamic changes in your life. Designed as a tool to work alongside the 64 Gene Keys, your Profile contains specific phrases and keywords that provide a starting point for in-depth contemplation and dialogue concerning the Gene Keys.\n[...]\nRichard Rudd reminds\n[...]\na process of inner\n[...]\n, therefore it\n[...]\nnot necessary to be too fixated on the\n[...]\npower of this\n[...]\nyour willingness to\n[...]\n- Many people have found great insights by using the book or 64 Ways audios as an “oracle”. You can randomly choose one of the 64 keys by drawing a card, throwing the i ching, or randomly open the book to a specific chapter and draw wisdom from the present moment.\n[...]\n- There are many beautiful decks and apps out there that reference the 64 hexagrams and can be used as an aid to contemplate the Gene Keys. Such as the Wisdom Keepers deck by Rosy Aronson, and the Gene Keys Synthesis Deck by Elijah Parker.\n[...]\n- You can\n\n---\n\nTitle: The Gene Keys (Special Anniversary Edition) by Richard Rudd: 9781786789709 | PenguinRandomHouse.com: Books\nURL: https://www.penguinrandomhouse.com/books/780287/the-gene-keys-special-anniversary-edition-by-richard-rudd/\nPublished: 2024-12-17T02:39:54.000Z\nAuthor: Ulli Allmendinger\nHighlights:\nThe Gene Keys (Special Anniversary Edition) by Richard Rudd: 9781786789709 | PenguinRandomHouse.com: Books Skip to Main Content (Press Enter)\n[...]\nThis is a limited edition of a hugely popular bestseller, presented in a luxury slipcase with high-end production finishes. The perfect keepsake for Gene Keys fans.A stunning luxury edition of this bestselling spiritual life companion. Combining Western astrology, the I Ching and the concept of genetic archetypes, these transformative teachings open a path for profound inner transformation, unlocking the potential for the miraculous possibilities that are encoded within our genetic makeup.Designed to help you decode your Gene Keys Profile (free from genekeys.com/free-profile), the book explains how to transform your specific “shadows”, or fear patterns, into creative gifts. On every page there is a key insight that helps you to see yourself and live your life in a more harmonious way. A visionary synthesis with many practical applications, logical yet with great poetic subtlety, The Gene Keys is a spiritual companion to contemplate over the course of a lifetime.This new, luxury edition, complete with slipcase, a ribbon, foiling and gilded edges, amounts to a special keepsake for Gene Keys fans to treasure.\n\n---\n\nTitle: Resources - Gene Keys\nURL: https://genekeys.com/resources/\nPublished: 2022-01-06T06:27:08.000Z\nAuthor: N/A\nHighlights:\nSince its publication in 2009, the Gene Keys book has continued to inspire people all around the world. Rooted in the same code as DNA it is a book that uncannily talks to our DNA. Many people report having powerful experiences from reading and contemplating the Gene Keys book. If you are new to the Gene Keys, you may wish to use the book in combination with the Golden Path Program and your Profile. These 3 tools together create a potent transformation that is undeniable. Here you can listen to the introduction to the book read by the Author, as well as purchase the rare Author’s edition or the new Audiobook read by Jennifer Dixon.\n[...]\nThe original ‘prima materia’ of the Gene Keys, the I Ching is a sacred Chinese text dating from around the 4th century BC. Many commentaries and versions of the I Ching exist and it is perhaps best known as a popular oracle. The Gene Keys are a natural culmination of all previous incarnations of the i Ching. They ultimately point to the truth that all sacred texts have their source inside us. The same truths intuitively grasped by the ancient sages can now be proven by modern genetics – that the universe is built upon natural codes and these codes can be deciphered and unlocked. The original I Ching was held in the highest esteem as a sacred text with the capacity to mirror living wisdom in every moment. Likewise the Gene Keys point us inwardly to seek the source of our suffering in our Shadows and guide us in transforming that suffering into creativity and freedom.\n[...]\nDiscover your individual path to Genius. What is your higher purpose? What are you here to do and how can you achieve it? Your Activation Sequence is a perfect place to begin your journey into the Gene Keys through the lens of your Profile. A beautiful, illuminating course with optional printed book.This sequence walks you step-by-step through the first four spheres of your personal Hologenetic Profile.\n[...]\n“In the great wheeling arc of the 64 Gene Keys, every Gene Key has an exact position in relationship to the cosmos and thus filters the cosmic stream as it enters our planetary system.” – Gene Key 11 The synthesis between the I Ching and Western Astrology compose the primary coordinates for the Gene Keys Transmission. The hexagrams of the I Ching are the fundamental 64 genetic archetypes that make up the Gene Keys, and their overlay onto the Astrological wheel gives the Gene Keys context into our personal lives. Click below to learn more about the role of Astrology in the Gene Keys.\n[...]\nto the world\n[...]\nof Awakening (and\n[...]\nthe Wisdom Keep\n[...]\ns visionary book the Gene Keys\n[...]\nof the 6"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_function_p7vw6nqjp2z9_1","session_id":"e7c48987-b5d5-4f27-9d18-efac56ac5754","uuid":"9a24f70c-7626-4cf2-ba12-ab545ba15e41","timestamp":"2026-06-11T15:02:30.796Z","subagent_type":"general-purpose","task_description":"Research I Ching 64 sources"}
